<title>JAPAN: Amnuay says will succeed in defending Thai baht.</title>
<headline>Amnuay says will succeed in defending Thai baht.</headline>
<dateline>TOKYO 1997-05-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>Finance Minister Amnuay Viravan said on Thursday that Thailand had been and would be successful in its efforts to defend the baht.  </p>
<p>&quot;We have support from all our friends,&quot; he told reporters as he left a seminar in Tokyo on Asia's future.</p>
<p>&quot;We have been successful and we will be successful,&quot; he said.</p>
<p>Thailand intervened on Wednesday to defend the baht against fresh market attacks and its central bank warned of more actions to counter market pressure on the currency.</p>
